sociated data by contacting us.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Opt-Out of Analytics</strong>: You can opt-out of analytics data collection by adjusting your device settings or using a tracking blocker.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Access and Correction</strong>: You can request access to or correction of your information by contacting us.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Changes to This Policy</strong></p>\r\n<p>We may update this policy from time to time. If we make significant changes, we\'ll notify you by posting a notice on our website or through in-app notifications &sup1;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><u>Update date: September 29, 2025</u></p>\r\n<p><strong>AI Face Swap Feature &amp; User Photo Data Usage</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>1. Introduction</strong><br>As part of our services, we have implemented the \"AI Face Swap\" feature, which enables users to be digitally transported to historic and iconic locations, integral to the cultural heritage of the UAE. To facilitate the functionality of this feature, users are required to upload a photograph.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. Collection and Processing of Personal Data</strong><br>By uploading a photograph for the \"AI Face Swap\" feature, the user expressly consents to the collection, storage, and processing of such photograph by the Fujairah Culture &amp; Media Authority (FCMA). The photograph shall be used solely for the purpose of enhancing, refining, and improving the AI model(s) powering the \"AI Face Swap\" feature.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. Data Storage and Transfer</strong><br>The user\'s photograph, along with any associated model data and derived outputs, shall be stored securely on FCMA&rsquo;s servers. Additionally, the data may be transferred to, and stored on, servers of third-party partners engaged by FCMA to facilitate efficient processing and usage of such data in relation to the \"AI Face Swap\" feature.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. Retention of Data</strong><br>The photograph and related model data will be retained by FCMA for as long as 